Package: R2PPT
Title: Simple R Interface to Microsoft PowerPoint using RDCOMClient
Suggests: RDCOMClient
Version: 2.2.0
Author: Wayne Jones <wayne.w.jones@shell.com>
Maintainer: Wayne Jones <wayne.w.jones@shell.com>
Description: R2PPT provides a simple set of wrappers to easily use 
         RDCOMClient for generating Microsoft PowerPoint presentations.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 2.3.0)
